snippet.title: Burning Skies Arcade - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Gamplay trailer for our upcoming retro indie game Burning Skies Arcade!

Coming to Steam on January 18th, wishlist now:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2290190/Burning_Skies_Arcade/
